g.text: Tri-Color Abstraction: Object States During Marking

ul.li: Black objects never point to white objects
Ensures no reachable object is missed

div.p: Next to process: Object B Will enqueue: D, E

ol.li:
While queue not empty: a. Dequeue object O (GRAY) b. For each child C of O:
If C is WHITE:
Mark C as GRAY
Enqueue C c. Mark O as BLACK

div.p: Incremental GC: Can pause/resume marking Concurrent GC: Mutator can run during marking Write barriers: Maintain invariants during mutation
Cost: Extra metadata per object (2 bits)
